{"title": "Blue Flower", "description": "\"Sometimes short stories are brought together like parcels in a basket. Sometimes they grow together like blossoms on a bush. Then, of course, they really belong to one another, because they have the same life in them. ...There is such a thought in this book. It is the idea of the search for inward happiness, which all men who are really alive are following, along what various paths, and with what different fortunes! Glimpses of this idea, traces of this search, I thought that I could see in certain tales that were in my mind,\u2014tales of times old and new, of lands near and far away. So I tried to tell them, as best as I could, hoping that other men, being also seekers, might find some meaning in them\" (Summary by from the preface)", "duration": 20312, "language": "English", "authors": [{"id": "836", "name": "Henry van Dyke"}], "coverArt": "https://archive.org/download/blueflower_1309_librivox/Blue_Flower_1309.jpg", "copyright_year": "1909", "genres": ["Single Author Collections"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "LibriVox Volunteers"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "Phil Chenevert"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "Phil Chenevert"}, {"role": "Proof Listener", "name": "ElleyKat"}], "sections": [{"section": 0, "title": "00 - PREFACE", "readers": [8033], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/blueflower_1309_librivox/blueflower_00_vandyke_64kb.mp3", "duration": 257}, {"section": 1, "title": "01 - THE BLUE FLOWER", "readers": [8033], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/blueflower_1309_librivox/blueflower_01_vandyke_64kb.mp3", "duration": 409}, {"section": 2, "title": "02 - THE SOURCE", "readers": [8051], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/blueflower_1309_librivox/blueflower_02_vandyke_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1932}, {"section": 3, "title": "03 - THE MILL", "readers": [8051], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/blueflower_1309_librivox/blueflower_03_vandyke_64kb.mp3", "duration": 2